TrainerBattles.Name: Newbie Bobby
TrainerBattles.StartLine: Check out my awesome first Pokemon!
TrainerBattles.EndLine: Aww man, it stopped moving. What do I do now?

TrainerBattles.Name: Enthusiastic Noob Steven
TrainerBattles.StartLine: I've been preparing for this day my whole life! I'll show you some tips.
TrainerBattles.EndLine: Maybe I got a little full of myself, I'll focus on the basics and become a great trainer one day!

TrainerBattles.Name: Rich Kid David
TrainerBattles.StartLine: My parents got me all the items I could ever need! Nobody can keep up with me!
TrainerBattles.EndLine: Wow, I guess being rich isn't enough by itself. I'll try harder next time!
